response.overview: "Come along for a musical journey with Janet and the kids! Youngsters will be entertained while they learn how to show respect for nature and others. You’ll love Fabulicious Day for its Christian Values. Kids will love to watch every episode again and again! Make every day a Fabulicious Day!"
